    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Suzaku Clan,</p><p>You have learned how to temper your flames allowing them to flicker but never die.</p><ul><li>Increase your Wisdom or Charisma score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>You now add your Charisma modifier to checks for maintaining concentration for jutsu with the fire release keyword.</li><li>Whenever you inflict the burned condition on a creature, the DC for putting out the flames is equal to the DC of your suzaku clan Hijutsu or 16, whichever is higher.</li></ul>",
